nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure

Class TypeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure.SolutionWorkflowNode
      • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure.TypeNode

  • public class TypeNode
extends SolutionWorkflowNode
    The TypeNode class is used to represent a data instance in the memory, in the actual solution workflow. Each TypeNode represents an output of a tool in the workflow execution.

    When compared to the TypeAutomaton representation of the problem, a Workflow TypeNode correspond to a State of a WorkflowElement.MEMORY_TYPE element.
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
